<view class="page-shell">
  <view class="page-content">
    <text class="eyebrow">ENNEAGRAM · 问心</text>
    <view class="page-title">九型人格<br />照见此心</view>
    <view class="page-subtitle">用几分钟照见惯性动作，再把它转成每日一件可练之事。</view>

    <view class="progress-card card">
      <view class="progress-head">
        <text>第 {{currentQuestion.no}} / {{questions.length}} 题</text>
        <button bindtap="restart">重测</button>
      </view>
      <view class="bar"><view style="width: {{progress}}%;"></view></view>
      <view class="dimension">{{currentQuestion.dimension}}</view>
    </view>

    <view class="question-card card">
      <view class="question-mark">问</view>
      <view class="question-text">{{currentQuestion.text}}</view>
      <view class="options">
        <button
          wx:for="{{options}}"
          wx:key="value"
          class="option {{selectedValue === item.value ? 'selected' : ''}}"
          data-value="{{item.value}}"
          bindtap="selectOption"
        >
          <text>{{item.label}}</text>
          <view>{{item.value}}</view>
        </button>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="split-actions">
      <button class="ghost-btn" bindtap="prev" disabled="{{currentIndex === 0}}">上一题</button>
      <button class="primary-btn" bindtap="next" disabled="{{selectedValue < 0}}">
        {{isLast ? '生成心证' : '下一题'}}
      </button>
    </view>

    <view class="assessment-note card">
      <text>照见边界</text>
      <view>本照见只用于照见交易人格倾向，帮助你匹配每日事上练。心证关注情绪触发、行为偏差和省察克治路径。</view>
    </view>

    <compliance-notice />
  </view>
  <bottom-tab-bar active="assessment" />
</view>
